nodes.text: Docking bay 77 was located in Mos Eisley on the planet Tatooine. It was owned and operated by the Sullustan Voos. Rai-Kalei berthed his ship, the Mayjeln there. The docking bay was owned by Voos, who made a few alterations to the docking bay. Keeping your ship here cost 2 credits a day. Restocking consumables cost 10 credits per one person's worth of supplies and Fuel cells were recharged at 10 credits per cell. A few minutes in the Refresher Booth cost 10 credits and a bad autochef meal cost 5 credits.
